Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  我不是英国人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是个如假包换的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别闹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的头发是染过的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还戴了美瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就没有过什么金色的要素啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝怎么这么一本正经的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.17,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}整人大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚人节？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚人节快乐  绫绫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是新学期了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:23.16,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(1425,570)\fad(500,500)}Episode3  \N灿烂夺目的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4月1号早过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要吓人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这不是愚人节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是扮愚人节而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扮愚人节？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为愚人节没骗够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以趁现在赶紧都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说英国的愚人节很热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻上还会报假的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国人很喜欢开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可怎么办？这可如何是好？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  敢问为何如此烦恼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把手表弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问现在是几点？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  确实还有大本钟可以看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说BBC上放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放BBC上去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家闹咋样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是除了4月1号以外骗人可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人可是要被阎王拔舌头的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌……舌头？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫绫你不也在骗人吗  这不公平！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是一种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎确实不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年一次也就罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家弟弟和妹妹经常说些非真非假的话混淆视听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然才小学4年级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢骗人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  他俩在学校里也很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被老师和朋友们称为“谎言双子”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点让人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羡慕？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来像乐队名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子你有亲兄弟姐妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有妹妹和弟弟两个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太和美月是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过他们俩小时候的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兄弟姐妹可真是让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我是姐姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子  你可是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好管管怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好管管？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这风是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们  骗人是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇什么哇  要说不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我为什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是猪熊空太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是美月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天转学来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比在场的各位小一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说慌说的这么溜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这么盯着我可是会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆…爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫骗人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说是很认生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来高中做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只有上午有课不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘带钥匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸妈上班去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要上一个小时的课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿我的钥匙赶紧回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问过保健室的阿姨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说我们可以在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给糊弄过去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是含泪求人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还是用眼药水骗过去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是忍  还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐受你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很懂事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是爱丽丝  你们好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  爱丽丝小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个  人家和我同岁的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们俩是来找你求援的  你就看开点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又不喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯只是忘记带钥匙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我可是爱着你们俩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们差不多该回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把她们带到保健室去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们下课了再来找你们  稍等一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们刚才那句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的心情我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然这是搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说不喜欢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐不懂幽默
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在英国住的话可能会碰钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不直接说出来她就不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们诚实一些她会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子只是个单纯的愣头青啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要是能那么懂的话我就不会遭那么多罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自问自答…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是罕见  阳子居然会没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子  振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个说的不是真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂是懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  是你最喜欢的漫画大肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太瞧不起我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为独生子女  我也很羡慕那种关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是兄弟姐妹吵架之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们来试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就是妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我受不了了  再也不要和你说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不太对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.98,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜大人  小的什么都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做也休想得到我的原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  可怜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:30.90,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.74,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,你很眼红？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.49,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是独生子女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个金发的妹妹真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你眼红的是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦和大家说一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太  美月  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方才真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其实很喜欢姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不能这么感动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好又是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐竟开始怀疑社会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩可真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心疼小绫姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们会提到绫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样才能如实的传达自己的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绫  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是小绫你经常说假话？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫其实是开玩笑的大师？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是英国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收我为徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能诚实地对阳子表白就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  绫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每天起的可真早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子的笑容就像太阳一样灿烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是但是  今天我一定要坦诚一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳…阳子  就像太阳一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说我太热血了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我〇…不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干啥呢这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝你行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦  爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不吃你这套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想养一条狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  昨晚看电视的时候正好有和狗相关的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝在英国有养一条大型犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不准备养吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得小狗还是很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但好像是条狗都会朝我叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是被鄙视了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让养狗的人家给爱丽丝摸一摸如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不用养也能把玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得忍家附近有人养狗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌龟我倒是在养
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌龟不太好逗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让她空欢喜一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来介绍下我家的宠物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什  什  什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子把我当成她的宠物了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  绫  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是中学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫看起来真的好像一条小狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总让人感觉想给她戴个项圈遛一遛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经有过这样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳…阳子竟会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此的变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子  你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个想法很正确  我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  从今天起我就是你的狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会伸爪也会陪着你散步的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情对我下命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想看到那样的忍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…没力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poppy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  爱丽丝想要疼爱狗狗的忍耐槽要爆表了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}只要我闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}我就会想起Poppy的软毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}As I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1080)}I can remember poppy's soft fur
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一说Poppy是爱丽丝在英国养的那条狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子头发的触感说不定可以替代Poppy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意  小绫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这打击够直接的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.19,zhushi1,NTP,0,0,0,,Poppy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她的头发很柔顺的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是和谐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像是小学生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是爱丽丝同学看起来真的很苦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九世桥老师  你能帮我拿一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为老师  我一定要帮助她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然做到这种地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音好像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师  有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好想学一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝同学在英国养了一条狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得乌丸老师有在养兔子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九世桥老师有养什么宠物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一条猫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是她的手机屏幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌丸老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学生面前不要说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为老师的尊严会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人会在动物面前一下变得柔和不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爸爸也老会摸家里乌龟的壳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人在家很寂寞吧  我们吃饭好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,795)}爱丽丝=兔子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我从学生那里收到饼干了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我太任性给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如再求求她宠物这件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我毕竟是寄住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养宠物对小孩的情感教育能起到帮助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对爱丽丝的成长也会有帮助的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我盯……………………
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子  我和你同岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是把我当小孩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我当然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养宠物  可以对小孩的情感教育能起到帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好管教的话  狗也不会乱叫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我拜托我的家人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他们会同意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍平日便充满着光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今日的你仿佛是太阳一般光芒四射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝居然能这么自然地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宠物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绫你有什么想要养的宠物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟儿之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要尝一尝烤鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤…鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问的时机不对  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟儿是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不需要养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在  一定要诚实而自然地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有宠物也有朋友和阳子你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来还有事  先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好羞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过刚才我的意思应该好好传达给她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是我就是宠物喽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是早上那件事的报复吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宠物？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会掉毛  还会给衣服沾上味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还要花钱养
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视上欣赏一下不就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  狗狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当是为了爱丽丝求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想  太  多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poppy？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得或许能让你打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个清扫器是姐姐买的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍和勇姐  谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太感激了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被叮嘱去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会见啊  Poppy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要我陪你去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我超有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带手帕了没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信号灯要等到绿的才能走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太和美月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你们两个在玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝也来陪我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还要去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你早起突然能说十二种语言是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听闻阳子成为一个勇者就要出门冒险去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要结婚  不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想和姐姐们一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息日还让你们上门真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你好像有事要忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绫姐姐现在很诚实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的金发比起金子还要贵重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还差得远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来夸夸阳子的优点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优点  优点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要会错意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.63,0:23:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳子没有作为姐姐的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始要叫我姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的袜子不配套
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的威严啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且发带也没带
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有带什么发带过！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
